License / Terms of Use


1. Data Source Disclaimer
All vehicle and auction data included in this repository are collected from public Australian car auction marketplaces. The underlying data, listings, and content remain the property of the original data providers.


2. Wholesale Console Rights
The compiled, aggregated, and anonymised analytics, including structured summaries, statistical distributions, weekly snapshots, and example vehicle records, are proprietary intellectual property of Wholesale Console.



3. Usage Terms
By using this dataset, you agree to:

Use the data for research, analysis, AI experimentation, or educational purposes.

Cite or link to this repository when referencing the dataset.

Respect any limitations described in the dataset schema or README.



4. Restricted Actions
You may not:

Reproduce, redistribute, or sell the raw underlying auction data.

Attempt to de-anonymise individual vehicles or reveal proprietary bidding/valuation methods.

Use the data for competitive scraping or commercial resale.



5. API Usage Advisory

The public API and dataset provide aggregated information only.

Use responsibly and in accordance with the rate limits and terms of service on the main application.

Full access to detailed listings, suggested bids, transport costs, and auction premiums requires an authenticated dashboard subscription.



6. Liability Disclaimer
Wholesale Console calculations are based on market estimations and doesn't imply the final order. Please consider market and your budget while making final decisions.
